#: 01804:9
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Hmm......\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Mmm...\""

#: 01804:10
msgid "I don't know why, but I suddenly stopped walking. But then again, I wasn't sure if I was really walking in the first place."
msgstr "No se por qué, pero he dejado de andar. Aunque la verdad no tengo claro siquiera que estuviese realmente andando."

#: 01804:11
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Wait a minute, where am I going?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Un momento. ¿Adónde estoy yendo?\""

#: 01804:12
msgid "Right, first question: Why am I even here? As I continued walking, I figured out that I didn't know where I was headed."
msgstr "Y para empezar, ¿qué hago aquí? Mientras caminaba me di cuenta de que no sabía adónde estaba yendo."

#: 01804:13
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Damn, I'm really out of it.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Joder. .\""

#: 01804:14
msgid "I looked around once more."
msgstr "Mire alrededor una vez más."

#: 01804:15
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Hmm?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Uhm?\""

#: 01804:16
msgid "That's......"
msgstr "Esa es..."

#: 01804:17
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Natsume-chan.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Natsume.\""

#: 01804:20
# Revisar.
msgid "Natsume-chan slowed turned towards me when I called her. Her movement was almost mechanical, like a doll. She would be as cute as a doll if she didn't speak."
msgstr "Cuando la llamé por su nombre, me saludó débilmente. Cuando me saluda, parece casi como una muñequita. Es muy mona si no dice nada."

#: 01804:21
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 01804:22
msgid "Even though she saw me, Natsume-chan didn't say anything, as usual."
msgstr "Aún habiéndome visto y como de costumbre, no me dice nada."

#: 01804:23
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What are you doing here all by yourself?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Qué estás haciendo aquí tú sola?\""

#: 01804:24
msgid "She's always alone. I'm worried about whether or not she really has any friends. I can't leave her on her own."
msgstr "Siempre va sola. Me preocupa que realmente no tenga maigos. No puedo dejarla sola."

#: 01804:27
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"It's you again. Why do you keep coming here, Haruma? Is it a choice, or...\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Eres tú otra vez. ¿Por qué has venido? ¿Has elegido venir aquí Haruma? O...\""

#: 01804:28
msgid "I could tell that she was really trying to decipher something about me when she looked into my eyes. It made me uncomfortable."
msgstr "Por su mirada, parece que esté tratando de averiguar algo sobre mí. Me resulta incómodo."

#: 01804:29
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What can I say? It's a small island and we both live here. I'm pretty sure that we're bound to run into each other every now and then, right?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Bueno. Es una isla pequeña y los dos vivimos en ella. ¿Es bastante probable encontrarnos, no?\""

#: 01804:32
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"............boring. Chatting with you is boring.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"...Me aburres. Tos conversaciones son siempre muy aburridas, Haruma.\""

#: 01804:33
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Well, I wasn't trying to be entertaining...\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Bueno, tampoco es que pretendiese resultar gracioso.\""

#: 01804:34
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"I see.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Ajá.\""

#: 01804:36
msgid "It seemed like she didn't care much, and she started walking away."
msgstr "Parece que no le importa mucho y empieza a caminar de nuevo."

#: 01804:38
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Where are you going?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Adónde vas?\""

#: 01804:41
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Why are you following me? It's best not to bother with me.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"¿Por qué me estás siguiendo? No te preocupes por mí.\""

#: 01804:42
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Don't say that. If you keep up that attitude where you try to keep people away, then one day there won't be anybody left around you.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No digas eso. Si sigues con esa actitud, evitando a la gente, llegará un día en que no habrá nadie a tu alrededor.\""

#: 01804:45
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 01804:48
msgid "I didn't know if what I said meant anything to her, but it definitely made her stop walking."
msgstr "No sé si las cosas que le he dicho han hecho algo, pero desde luego ha servido para que se parase."

#: 01804:49
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Huh? Natsume-chan?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Eh? ¿Natsume?\""

#: 01804:50
msgid "She stared at me with her back still facing me. I think she's angry."
msgstr "Todavía no se ha girado a mirarme. Parece que se ha enfadado."

#: 01804:51
# Revisar. ¿Cambiar "brusca" por "haberlo dicho de una forma que te haya molestado"?
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I'm sorry. I think I said that in a way that upset you. I apologize.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Lo siento. Creo que lo he dicho de una forma un tanto brusca. Lo siento.\""

#: 01804:54
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"No, it's OK. Maybe you're right.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"No, no pasa nada. Quizá tengas razón.\""

#: 01804:55
msgid "I was surprised. Normally she wouldn't accept anything I said. This really isn't like her."
msgstr "Estaba sorprendido. Generalmente no habría tolerado lo que he dicho. No es propio de ella."

#: 01804:56
msgid "Maybe I said something I shouldn't have?"
msgstr "Quizá he dicho algo que no debería haber dicho."

#: 01804:57
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Um... I'm really sorry about what I said. Are you mad at me?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Eh... Siento de veras lo que he dicho. ¿No estás enfadada?\""

#: 01804:60
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"I'm not really mad, but...\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"No estoy enfadada, pero...\""

#: 01804:61
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"But?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Pero?\""

#: 01804:62
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Maybe it's my fault, like you said, and that's why Papa left me.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Tenías razón en lo que has dicho. Quizá es por eso que mi padre desapareció delante de mí.\""

#: 01804:63
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Papa?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Padre?\""

#: 01804:64
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 01804:65
msgid "Although Natsume-chan was right in front of me, her back seemed very small and distant. It was the first time I'd ever heard her mention her family."
msgstr "Tras escuchar lo del padre de Natsume por primera vez, parecía como si Natsume estuviese muy lejos de mí pese a estar justo delante mío."

#: 01804:66
msgid "I didn't know what was going on, but I was sure that I hurt Natsume-chan's feelings somehow."
msgstr "No sabía exáctamente lo que estaba pasando, pero estaba seguro de que había herido los sentimientos de Natsume de alguna forma."

#: 01804:67
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Natsume-chan......\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Natsume...\""

#: 01804:71
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"It's fine. Don't worry about it. I'm all right by myself.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"No te preocupes por eso. Estoy bien sola.\""

#: 01804:73
msgid "She started walking off again, so I chased after her."
msgstr "Empezó a caminar de nuevo, así que fuí tras ella."

#: 01804:76
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Nothing is going to happen, even if you follow me.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"No va a pasar nada aunque me sigas.\""

#: 01804:77
# <es>{Kazushi}\n"No. Iré contigo. Do you think I would let people that who says that their alrite alone go?"
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No, I'll go with you. Do you honestly think I'd just let someone who says she's fine on her own go without someone else beside her?\""
msgstr ""

#: 01804:80
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"I told you, I'm okay. Stop being nosy.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Ya te lo he dicho. Estoy bien. Deja de fisgonear.\""

#: 01804:81
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Then since I'm nosy, let me ask a nosy question: where did your Papa go, Natsume-chan?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Me da igual ser un entrometido. Y por eso, ¿puedo hacerte una pregunta entrometida? ¿Dónde está tu padre?\""

#: 01804:84
msgid "I knew it was a personal question, but I just couldn't help trying to find out more about her. She heaved an exasperated sigh."
msgstr "Sabía que era una pregunta muy personal, pero no pude evitar querer saber más de ella."

#: 01804:87
# Revisar. ¿Cambiar "preocupas" por "querer saber"?
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"You really are nosy. Why do you care so much about me?\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Eres un fisgón de verdad. ¿Por qué te preocupas tanto por mí?\""

#: 01804:88
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What do you mean \"why\"?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿A qué te refieres con \"por qué\"...?\""
